ygData.subject: New graphics?
ygData.msgSnippet: I logged in for a bit and I noticed that my Skull of Jhen tra (sp?) looked like a voodoo doll. I m glad that they re adding some more graphics to things
ygData.messageBody:
I logged in for a bit and I noticed that my Skull of Jhen'tra (sp?) looked
like a voodoo doll. I'm glad that they're adding some more graphics to things
(anyone else notice another new graphic) but all they're doing is copying
other graphics! All they did was copy the graphic of a wooden totem and they
made the skull look like it. I don't know if I should interpret this is as a
good sign or a bad one.
Just thought I'd let you guys know.
